data.description: This 3 Bedroom W/ 2 Full Bathroom Home Is Immaculate & Full Of Upgrades! Enjoy The Open Floor Plan W/ High Ceilings & Large Windows Throughout. The Beautiful Kitchen Is The Heart Of The Home Complete With Large Customized Quartz Countertop,  Island & Stainless Steel Appliances. Updated Lighting Throughout The Entire Home. Fully Updated Guest Bathroom And Laundry Room. This Floorplan Includes two dining areas, a private office, , Large Extended Patio For Entertaining Right Off The Living Area. The Large Master Bedroom W/ Large Garden Tub, Double Sinks & Walk-In Closet. Enjoy The Fully Fenced Backyard Perfect For Kids & Pets with a covered patio slab. Convenient location on major highways (I-35/410/1604/Wurzbach Pwky) close to shops and restaurants, Randolph AFB and Fort Sam Houston.
